Tournament: <%= @tournament.name %>
Event: <%= @event %>
Branch: <%= @payload[:branch_name].presence || @tournament.branch&.name || "N/A" %>

<% if @event == "match_scored" %>
A tournament match result has been recorded.

Match ID: <%= @payload[:match_id] %>
Winner Team ID: <%= @payload[:winner_id] %>
<% elsif @event == "tournament_registration_created" %>
A new tournament registration has been submitted and is waiting for review.

Registration ID: <%= @payload[:registration_id] %>
Player ID: <%= @payload[:player_id] %>
Player Name: <%= @payload[:player_name] %>
Player Phone: <%= @payload[:player_phone] %>
Player Email: <%= @payload[:player_email].presence || "N/A" %>
Skill Level: <%= @payload[:player_skill_level].presence || "N/A" %>
Status: <%= @payload[:status].to_s.humanize %>
Moderation Link: <%= @payload[:moderation_url].presence || "Not configured" %>
<% elsif @event == "registration_status_changed" %>
A tournament registration status has changed.

Registration ID: <%= @payload[:registration_id] %>
Player ID: <%= @payload[:player_id] %>
Player Name: <%= @payload[:player_name] %>
Player Phone: <%= @payload[:player_phone] %>
Player Email: <%= @payload[:player_email].presence || "N/A" %>
New Status: <%= @payload[:status].to_s.humanize %>
Moderation Link: <%= @payload[:moderation_url].presence || "Not configured" %>
<% else %>
A tournament event has occurred.
<% end %>

Timestamp: <%= Time.current.iso8601 %>
